Interface RVOnClickListener.OnItemClickListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NotificationFragment, UpdateActivity
    Enclosing class:

    public static interface RVOnClickListener.OnItemClickListener
    This interface contains two methods one for item click and another for long press/click on item. These methods will be invoked whenever user touched on the position of RecyclerView's item
